               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17830115-7-cd50" type="crimeDate">9th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830115-7-off49 t17830115-7-cd50"></join> last, one lump of sugar containing twenty-three pounds and an half, value 18 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830115-7-victim127" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Adams
